{"tid":1033092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2其實047香港會點","createTime":"2019-02-23T00:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T02:51:40.000Z","uid":15010,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"83eb9f2738bb30143a01beb49192626fb6adb043","tid":1033092,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:31:11.000Z","msg":"基本法只係寫50年不變<br />\n先唔好講可信性，字面上只係得返28年<br />\n<br />\n究竟28年後會點？<br />\n變成一個普通中國城市？好似上海咁？<br />\n岀國用中國護照？<br />\n拆關？<br />\n行中國法律？<br />\n<br />\n點解時間得返咁少但好似冇乜聲氣咁<br />\n定係個d乜鳩大灣區已經係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faac93423f9957131823bf6fa9a352fd865aecbd","tid":1033092,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:32:49.000Z","msg":"如果公眾假期跟中國會唔會暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19545917dfe9b202068106215f1bb2460ca5d9ec","tid":1033092,"uid":154054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:46:10.000Z","msg":"到時就算乜都唔做都已經係全部大陸人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3564077be3c9be78a4f0569b4190ed2ec6b761","tid":1033092,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"其實係冇分別<br />\n事關英中聯合聲明的而且同支那講嘅一樣，係歷史文件<br />\n係用嚟呃香港返嚟<br />\n講嘅50年不變只係「資本主義及原有生活方式」唔係成份嘢嘅限期<br />\n就算講「最終達至普選」都係冇時限<br />\n連佢拆關都唔洗理嗰50年，因為基本法都係冇時限<br />\n所以2047根本只係一個假限期，唔知當初咩人要呃香港人依樣嘢"},{"pid":"01b15bc68f177e4620de5392809700da1d0532b5","tid":1033092,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:15:44.000Z","msg":"香港政府d錢收歸國有，政府全部空降"},{"pid":"4f1f989339769d75688b6fd6930595230cd77a3e","tid":1033092,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:38:08.000Z","msg":"所有住緊嘅屋補地價<br />\n仲要好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d420a0726f1d4b6e7af13c5b20522dd09af02d63","tid":1033092,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit